          "description": "<p>There is&#160; free early learning and childcare provision for 3 and 4 year olds.&#160; Some 2 year olds are also eligible.&#160; For information on what is available and how to apply, see<b>&#160;&#160;</b><a href=\"https://www.sheffield.gov.uk/home/schools-childcare/childcare-free-early-learning.html\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>&#160;&#160;</p><p>The Sheffield Directory has information on <a href=\"http://www.sheffielddirectory.org.uk/kb5/sheffield/directory/advice.page?id=SjgNx3M3KoU\" target=\"_blank\">Childcare Options</a></p><p><span>This government </span><a href=\"http://childcarechoices.gov.uk\" target=\"\">web site</a><b>&#160;&#160;</b><span>has information about getting help with childcare costs.</span><br></p><p><br></p>",
