                      "description": "<p>Citizens Advice Sheffiedl&#160; provides advice, support and information about housing, employment, family reunion, immigration, renewals and settlement applications and discrimination.  They have a central office in the Circle and local branches across the city</p><p>.For a full list of smaller local branches and their opening hours see the leaflet in printable resources.&#160;</p><p><b>Coronavirus update:&#160;<span>Due to the impact of Coronavirus, in order to protect both clients, staff and volunteers, we are not opening any face to face services across the city.</span>&#8203;&#8203;See here for advice lines&#160;<a href=\"https://citizensadvicesheffield.org.uk/\" target=\"_blank\">https://citizensadvicesheffield.org.uk/</a></b><br><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>",
