          "id": 51,
          "name": "English Language Classes (ESOL) and Online Resources for Learning English",
          "description": "<p><b>Covid 19 Update 24.08.2020</b></p><p>The <b>WEA</b> have announced their ESOL provision for Autumn 2020. See printable resources for the timetable.&#160;&#160;</p><table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">  <tbody><tr>   <td width=\"601\">   <p>To register visit <a href=\"https://www.wea.org.uk/\">https://www.wea.org.uk/</a> or call their support centre at 0300   3033464 Support Centre open weekdays 8am &#8211; 8pm.   Saturday 8am &#8211; 1pm</p>   </td>  </tr> </tbody></table><p><b>Learn for Life Enterprises&#160;</b><span>also have places on ESOL for the Autumn term. You can register via this&#160;</span><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdMcRWSdPHN6JvOzJDVpv43hUkNZRLf7Rjjq3Cy38302As8fA/viewform?usp=sf_link\" target=\"\">form</a><span>.</span></p><p></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p></p>",
          "event": "<p>Printable resources contains details of upcoming courses.</p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span>For those who want to meet face-to-face (outdoors observing social distancing),</span><span><span>&#160;</span></span><span>Conversation Club is meeting every Friday at 13:00 at Sheffield Botanical Gardens.&#160;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The session includes an English class at 2pm for an hour (for those who want to).&#160;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Join for friendly, informal conversation. Children are welcome too.&#160;</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>",
