                      "description": "U-Mix Centre is a youth and community centre managed by Football Unites, Racism Divides (FURD).  Facilities include: football pitches, dance studio, recording studio, digital media centre, fitness suite, training and performance suite, activity room, and meeting rooms.  Organisations can rent these facilities to host sports activities and dance classes etc.",
