                      "description": "<p><b>Coronavirus update: closed other then for 1 to 1 appointments.&#160; See details <a href=\"https://www.togetherwomen.org/covid-19\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>&#160;</b></p><p><br></p><p>Sheffield Together Women Project provides holistic and gender-specific support to vulnerable women across the city of Sheffield. The centre has a women-only facility in the heart of Sheffield that offers a safe and welcoming place for women to engage in meaningful support and community services, all under one roof.                     Our flexible and creative approach allows us to provide innovative ways to engage with women who may be hard to reach, or who are struggling to access mainstream services.</p><p>To contact via e-mail use this online form:&#160;<a href=\"https://www.togetherwomen.org/contact-us\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">togetherwomen.org/contact-us</a></p><p>Their timetable of activities is <a href=\"https://www.togetherwomen.org/whats-on\" target=\"\">here</a>.</p><p><br></p>",
