          "name": "Low cost/free Household items, furniture, white goods",
          "description": "<p><b>St Vincent's Furniture Store Sheffield </b>can deliver household items and small electrical items free of charge. A referral has to be made by a registered agency. A list of registered agencies is <a href=\"http://www.svpfurniturestoresheffield.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/AGENCY-LIST-FOR-WEBSITE.pdf\" target=\"\">here.</a>&#160;</p><p><b>The Besom in Sheffield</b>&#160;&#8203;may be able to provide and deliver items for free. Referral form in printable resources, this form should only be used by a social worker or other professional.</p><p>Search <a href=\"https://www.gumtree.com/freebies/sheffield\" target=\"\">Sheffield Gumtree</a>&#160;or <a href=\"https://groups.freecycle.org/group/SheffieldUK/posts/all\" target=\"\">Sheffield Freecycle</a> for free items which will have to be collected.</p><p><br></p>",
