                      "id": 364,
                      "name": "Clover Group - The Mulberry Practice",
                      "description": "<p>Mulberry Practice (Specialist Asylum seeker GP practice) offers primary care services to refugees and asylum seekers residing in Sheffield, but people may choose to register with another local GP.</p><p>Opening times Monday-Friday 8:30am-6:00pm.</p>",
